Path Downstream



This path continues downstream from our campsite for a few hundred yards until running into a mass of no trespassing signs. Other campers came through periodically.
Taken Sunday, June 24, 2001, 03:29:29pm.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 1020kb
Technical details: Olympus C700UZ, 1/30s @ F2.8, ISO 200, 50mm
